dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:11:56.000Z","msg":"好方便喎，揸車出尖咀佐敦個頭完全唔洗塞車，係巴士線無選擇搞到嘥咗個轉車站"},{"pid":"ad4ea33f04a3f6f5c47a3abeda05ac413fe89386","tid":2494034,"uid":344249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:15:36.000Z","msg":"你諗下A41/A41P果堆都唔行青沙就知唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db993d911662dde56439dd7f172a83f5092c1cb3","tid":2494034,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:18:20.000Z","msg":"其實另一個問題係T4未設計/起好<br />\n大埔公路沙田段繁忙時間就例塞<br />\n青沙去沙田方向一係顯田出 一係大埔公路沙田段<br />\n平時繁忙時間得顯田出口唔會塞<br />\n但落到去大圍又要揸一段路先上返高速<br />\n冇咁吸引"},{"pid":"bd41cd5bed2dae39ef618d00d10863573a37940d","tid":2494034,"uid":14787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"其實最戇鳩係沙田出入口位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到尖山隧道係好快，但問題係前段塞到去馬場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九龍返黎個出口又join埋城隧出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d68e1014ef5f2d209b2c1d0013e5540f9f8a388","tid":2494034,"uid":26418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ad4ea33f04a3f6f5c47a3abeda05ac413fe89386","tid":2494034,"uid":344249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:15:36.000Z","msg":"你諗下A41/A41P果堆都唔行青沙就知唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:21:56.000Z","msg":"得A47X谷大里數繼續行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n249X都寧願行南橋+3號幹線+呈祥道"}]}